ses in Vietnam|mini=1|nodiv=1}})}}\n{{Template:Details of first 250 COVID-19 confirmed cases in Vietnam}}\n{{collapse bottom}}\n{{Clear}}\n\n{{clear}}\n<div class=\"toccolours\" style=\"display:inline-block; width:750px; margin:1em 0;\"><center>'''No. of confirmed cases, active cases and recoveries'''</center>\n{{Graph:Chart\n | width = 600\n | height = 240\n | type = line\n | yGrid =\n | xGrid =\n | legend = \n | colors = #376AB1, #3E9651, #CC2528\n | y1Title = Total Cases\n | y2Title = Recoveries\n | y3Title = Active Cases\n | xAxisAngle = -40\n | x = 01-23, 01-30, 02-06, 02-13, 02-20, 02-27, 03-06, 03-13, 03-20, 03-27, 04-03, 04-10, 04-17, 04-18\n | y1 = 2,5,12,16,16,16,17,47,91,163,237,257,268,268\n | y2 = 0,0,3,7,15,16,16,16,17,20,85,144,198,201\n | y3 = 2,5,9,9,1,0,1,31,74,143,152,113,70,67\n}}</div>\n\n<div class=\"toccolours\" style=\"display:inline-block; width:750px; margin:1em 0;\"><center>'''Growth rate of confirmed cases from 6 March 2020 ([[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Vietnam#Preventive measures|phase 2]])'''<br />(a rising straight line indicates exponential growth, while a horizontal line indicates linear growth)</center>\n{{Switcher|\n{{GraphChart\n|type=line\n|linewidth=2\n|showSymbols=1\n|width=600\n|colors={{Medical cases chart/Bar colors|3}}\n|showValues=\n|xAxisTitle=Total confirmed cases\n|xAxisAngle=-60\n|xScaleType=log\n|x=17, 20, 30, 31, 34, 38, 44, 47, 53, 57, 61, 66, 76, 85, 91, 94, 113, 123, 134, 141, 153, 163, 174, 188, 203, 207, 218, 227, 237, 240, 241, 245, 249, 251, 255, 257, 258, 260, 265, 266, 267, 268, 268, 268\n|yAxisTitle=Active cases\n|y=1, 4, 14, 15, 18, 22, 28, 31, 37, 41, 45, 50, 60, 69, 74, 77, 96, 106, 117, 124, 136, 143, 153, 163, 148, 149, 155, 152, 152, 150, 150, 150, 127, 125, 127, 113, 114, 116, 120, 97, 96, 91, 70, 67\n|yGrid= |xGrid= \n}}\n|Show logarithmic scale|\n{{GraphChart\n|type=line\n|linewidth=2\n|showSymbols=1\n|width=650\n|colors={{Medical cases chart/Bar colors|3}}\n|showValues=\n|xAxisTitle=Total confir